{"tid":135721,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[神知] 神大人 桂木桂馬 現實世界版","createTime":"2017-02-26T14:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T16:09:20.000Z","uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3488353b7cec6ed2760e750e6f2ce60e0fb926","tid":135721,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/02/26/shuno-kagura/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F02%2F26%2Fshuno-kagura%2F&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5b671384\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/02/26/shuno-kagura/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/kagura2.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fkagura2.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=477ca112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有許多人對愛玩遊戲的宅男都有著刻板印象，諸如在髒亂狹小的房間裡玩電動，但是 Kagura 這位日本男子的房子可是相當讓人肅立起敬啊 ! 他今年 39 歲，身為一位影片與遊戲出租連鎖店的店長，本人為遊戲控的他曾經用 10 個不同帳號來玩《 Final Fantasy XI 》，此事也讓他在日本的遊戲網站上一戰成名，而他自小便是《 Final Fantasy XI 》和《 Dragon Quest 》這兩個名作的粉絲，因此收藏了數量可觀的相關系列遊戲和周邊產品，但收藏品與日俱增，於是他便在自己的房子中展現了超強又有系統的收納術，來珍藏了他無數的遊戲機、螢幕、搖桿、漫畫、書籍與公仔，而這樣的另類住宅是不是讓你對宅男更加另眼相看了呢 !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/kagura1.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fkagura1.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=3c6223f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c261c4d98b8729c3ada27c1a203bd0f21a2ee84","tid":135721,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/kagura12.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F